name: The dense control consumes the will
description:
The pressure is constant, I don't know what to do.
I hear voices, they tell me that everything will be fine but I can feel their terror.
I stumble and I don't feel like getting up anymore, it seems that something hit me in a place where I don't get to see.
It's hard for me to decide on the simplest things.
Im quit.

By Rotten_ttc
